## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **belzutifan Welireg 2021/2023** = first FDA HIF-2α inhibitor. 2021 VHL syndrome (cross-inherited_adult) → 2023 mRCC LITESPARK-005. PAS-B pocket allosteric inhibition of HIF-2α dimerization with HIF-1β. quantum-VQE 의 PPI + allosteric pocket scaffold 직접 fit.
2. **sorafenib 2005 + sunitinib 2006** = first + second multi-kinase TKI mRCC — IFN/IL-2 immunotherapy 시대 종료. 2005 paradigm shift = VEGFR + multi-kinase frontline.
3. **nivolumab + ipilimumab 2018 (CheckMate 214)** = first FDA dual IO 1L intermediate/poor risk mRCC. 만성 IO+IO 시대 시작.
4. **pembrolizumab + axitinib 2019 (KEYNOTE-426) + nivolumab + cabozantinib 2021 (CheckMate 9ER) + pembrolizumab + lenvatinib 2021 (KEYNOTE-581) + avelumab + axitinib 2019 (JAVELIN Renal 101)** = IO + TKI 4 combo 1L paradigm. all-risk frontline 변화.
5. **cabozantinib Cabometyx 2016** = multi-kinase VEGFR + MET + AXL — sunitinib 후 progression 표준. 만성 sequencing post-IO 표준.
6. **temsirolimus 2007 + everolimus 2009** = mTOR axis mRCC — IO 시대 도래 후 후순위. 만성 transplant + TSC cross-link.
7. **pembrolizumab adjuvant 2021 (KEYNOTE-564)** = first FDA RCC adjuvant intermediate-high-risk post-nephrectomy. 만성 surgical paradigm 변화.
8. **IL-2 high-dose 1992** = historical durable response 일부 — toxicity 심각. 현대 IO checkpoint 가 대체.
9. **VHL syndrome belzutifan 2021** = inherited adult RCC + retinal hemangioblastoma + pheochromocytoma — first systemic therapy disease-modifying inherited cancer syndrome. cross-inherited_adult.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, RCC + mRCC + VHL 임상 의미 한정.

